# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if having platform-specific dependencies or dependencies
#   having no cross-platform support, pipenv may have dependencies that are not installable by others.
#   We recommend not committing Pipfile.lock to version control.
#   See: https://pipenv.pypa.io/en/latest/advanced/#ignoring-pipfile-lock-in-version-control
Pipfile.lock

# PEP 582; used by e.g. github.com/David-OConnor/pyflow and github.com/microsoft/pyright
